706.008, consumer finance company licensed under ORS chapter 725, mortgage banker or mortgage
broker licensed under ORS 86A.095 to 86A.198, or title company for business purposes, records de-
scribed in paragraph (a) of this subsection, if the exemption from disclosure of the records is sought
